\q1
\v 3 ThereforeВҰ364313 the land mourns,
\q1 and everyoneВҰ364320 who lives in it is wasting away,
\q1 along withВҰ364323 the animalsВҰ364324 in the countrysideВҰ364325 and the birds in the sky.
\q1 Even the fish in the seaВҰ364331 \add вүҲwill disappear\add*.
