\q1
\v 8 Blow the horn in GibeahВҰ364666,
\q1 and the trumpetВҰ364667 in Ramah.
\q1 Sound the alarm atВҰ364666 Beyt-Aven:
\q1 вҖҳWe'll follow youВҰ364672 \add into battle\add*, Benyamin!вҖҷ
\q1
\v 9 Efrayim\add /YisraelВҰ364681\add* will becomeВҰ364677 \add вүҲuninhabited inВҰ364680 the time\add* of punishment.
\q1 Among Yisrael's tribesВҰ364680 I declare what will certainly \add happen\add*.
\b
